name: Dark side of the Moon (Black)-Necklace
description:
This gorgeous necklace can be used as a meditation mala or just a gorgeous accessory. The thread is in Black and the beads are rudruksha.
 ( See Description below ) 

Also the clear crystal and black beaded necklace with orange thread goes perfect with this necklace. 

Buy as a combo or separate 

MEANINGS...

Sacred Rudraksha beads, Sanskrit, have been worn by Sages and Yogis since Vedic times for their profound spiritual significance and powerful healing properties. 

Sacred Rudraksha beads are seeds from the Rudraksha tree and according to ancient Vedic texts, these beads are endowed with cosmic powers to elevate the soul and assist on the path of ascension. 

By meditating with a Rudraksha mala or by wearing rudraksha against the skin, it is believed to increase the ability to concentrate, giving clarity and peace of mind, improve memory and relieve stress and anxiety. 

Rudraksha is also known to slow the aging process, increase stamina, reduce blood pressure, strengthen the heart and balances the nervous system. Not only that but the auspicious Rudraksha beads are believed to bestow divine protection and increase abundance and prosperity.

name: Journey to the Goddess Within - Journal with Coaching & Support
description:
If you have been searching for something more in your life then this guided journal is the missing link. It only takes 15 minutes a day. 

This journal will guide you through all the fluff and busyness of your life and have you reconnecting again with who you are. 

Not one for the faint hearted this journey takes, effort, commitment and truth on your part. 

If you are ready to reconnect all the lost parts of you then this is the path you have been looking for. 

It's time to choose YOU.

This Book comes to you as a PDF to print out and requires you to do work at your own pace. If you feel like you need a little support or push to stay on path then maybe look at purchasing the journal with coaching sessions 
OR 
Why not get together with some girlfriends and do it together. 

For extra support this package has personal coaching with it. 
Working together once a week for 2 weeks to guide and support you through the process. 

Extra coaching sessions can be purchased if needed.
